                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Sleeper</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-09-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 7, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Sleeper reports that insurgents have destroyed two culverts of Western
                    Railway between towns of Pinar del Rio and San Luis and interrupted traffic. He
                    also says that emissary left for Pinar del Rio on behalf of veterans to induce
                    Pino Guerra to suspend hostilities pending discussion peace negotiations.)</p>
            </div>
